An aircraft belonging to the Nigerian Air Force has crashed in Kaduna.

According to exclusive reports gathered by National Daily, the aircraft was on a flight demonstration in preparation for an air show being planned by the Airforce for next month.

As at the time of putting together National Daily further gathered that the remains of the Officers who hail from Gombe and Yobe states respectively have been taken to the military hospital morgue.

It was immediately clear what may have led to the crash.
